'''傑巴利采韋戰役'''（{{lang-uk|Бої за Дебальцеве}}）是[[頓巴斯戰爭|頓巴斯戰爭]]的其中一場戰役，自2015年1月起交戰雙方在[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]][[頓涅茨克州|頓涅茨克州]]的[[傑巴利采韋|傑巴利采韋]]附近爆發戰鬥。此地於2014年7月起一些地方開始被政府軍收復，分離主義者試圖奪回而發動攻擊。

傑巴利采韋在戰前的形勢如同[[楔子|楔子]]，一邊面對[[頓涅茨克人民共和國|頓涅茨克人民共和國]]，另一邊則是[[盧甘斯克人民共和國|盧甘斯克人民共和國]]<ref name=BBC23>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-31018092|title=US warns of more sanctions on Russia|date=2015-01-28|accessdate=2015-01-28|publisher=BBC|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108100043/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-31018092|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此處也是鐵路與公路的要衝。

== 背景 ==
經過[[2014年烏克蘭革命|2014年烏克蘭革命]]，烏克蘭東部陸續爆發[[2014年烏克蘭親俄羅斯武裝衝突|衝突]]。2014年4月，傑巴利采韋被親俄分離主義者所佔領，但到了7月28日政府軍成功收復此地，此後直至2015年1月皆穩固地控制著<ref name="IF28Ju">{{cite news | url=http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/215712.html | title=ATO forces take over Debaltseve, Shakhtarsk, Torez, Lutuhyne, fighting for Pervomaisk and Snizhne underway - ATO press center | work=Interfax-Ukraine News Agency | date=2014-07-28 | accessdate=2015-01-30 | archive-date=2014-07-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728192109/http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/215712.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然雙方簽下[[明斯克協議|明斯克協議]]確認停火，但在傑巴利采韋一帶仍間歇性發生衝突<ref name="OSCE15se">{{cite press release | url=http://www.osce.org/ukraine-smm/123587 | title=Spot report by the OSCE Special Monitoring Mission to Ukraine (SMM), 15 September 2014: Monitoring to the east of Donetsk, SMM patrol vehicles hit by fire | publisher=Organization for Security and Co-operation in Europe | date=2014-09-15 | accessdate=2015-01-30 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014117/https://www.osce.org/ukraine-smm/123587 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ada2">{{cite press release | url=http://www.ohchr.org/EN/NewsEvents/Pages/DisplayNews.aspx?NewsID=15143&LangID=E#sthash.cgVdJ2LL.dpuf | title=Protracted conflict in eastern Ukraine continues to take heavy toll on civilians | publisher=United Nations Office of the High Commissioner for Human Rights | date=2014-10-08 | accessdate=2015-01-30 | archive-date=2019-05-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531025754/https://www.ohchr.org/EN/NewsEvents/Pages/DisplayNews.aspx?NewsID=15143&LangID=E#sthash.cgVdJ2LL.dpuf | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 過程 ==
2015年1月，數千名烏克蘭政府軍駐紮於傑巴利采韋地區<ref name=KP@#4/>。此城為鐵路和公路的重要連結點，形勢對於政府軍就像「口袋」、「楔子」。於此之前的數個月，此地屢屢遭到砲擊，當地居民多數已經離開，商店、學校及住屋也關門或毀棄<ref name=KP@#4/>。1月17日開始，砲火愈趨猛烈，直到1月20日才暫時歇息<ref name=KP@#4>{{cite news|url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/kremlin-backed-separatists-rain-death-down-on-debaltseve-377923.html|title=Kremlin-backed separatists rain death down on Debaltseve|work=Kyiv Post|date=2015-01-20|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-date=2015-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711083831/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/kremlin-backed-separatists-rain-death-down-on-debaltseve-377923.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月22日，頓涅茨克人民共和國的軍隊向傑巴利采韋一帶的政府軍營地攻擊<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/kyiv-reports-russian-led-insurgents-attacks-in-debaltseve-sector-378087.html|title = Kyiv reports Russian-led insurgents attacks in Debaltseve sector|date = 2015-01-22|work = Kyiv Post|access-date = 2015-01-29|archive-date = 2015-11-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151127063924/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/kyiv-reports-russian-led-insurgents-attacks-in-debaltseve-sector-378087.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>，強烈的砲火持續至隔天仍未停止，但政府軍依舊死守營地<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.france24.com/en/20150123-video-ukraine-military-defend-strategic-eastern-town-debaltseve-pro-russia-separatists/|title = Video: The fight to defend Ukraine’s strategic Debaltseve|date = 23 January 2014|publisher = France 24|access-date = 29 January 2015|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150124123633/http://www.france24.com/en/20150123-video-ukraine-military-defend-strategic-eastern-town-debaltseve-pro-russia-separatists/|archive-date = 2015-01-24|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。在戰鬥中一所學校被砲彈擊中，而政府軍也朝分離主義者營地砲擊以示報復<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.kyivpost.com/multimedia/photo/shelled-kindergarden-in-debaltseve-378186.html|title = No one hurt as empty kindergarten gets shelled in Debaltseve|date = 2015-01-23|work = Kyiv Post|access-date = 2015-01-29|archive-date = 2017-10-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171019035528/https://www.kyivpost.com/multimedia/photo/shelled-kindergarden-in-debaltseve-378186.html/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。1月23日，頓涅茨克軍隊試圖收復三面受敵的傑巴利采韋。根據1月24日的報導，一個政府軍的檢查哨直接受到攻擊<ref>{{cite news |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |title=Tank troops fight to contain rebel expansion in eastern Ukraine |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/ukraine/11367411/Tank-troops-fight-to-contain-rebel-expansion-in-eastern-Ukraine.html |newspaper=The Telegraph |date=2015-01-24 |access-date=2015-01-29 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108095332/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/ukraine/11367411/Tank-troops-fight-to-contain-rebel-expansion-in-eastern-Ukraine.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1月25日，另一個位在傑巴利采韋附近的檢查哨也被襲擊，但被政府軍擊退。1月26日，隨著戰鬥持續，戰火蔓延至傑巴利采韋全區，一位居民告訴[[路透社|路透社]]傑巴利采韋幾乎已被分離主義者包圍，然而政府軍仍抵擋住接連的攻勢<ref>{{cite news |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |title=Ukraine rebels move to encircle government troops in new advance |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/01/26/us-ukraine-crisis-military-idUSKBN0KZ0L920150126 |agency=Reuters |date=2015-01-26 |access-date=2015-01-29 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924212850/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/01/26/us-ukraine-crisis-military-idUSKBN0KZ0L920150126 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 分離主義者進展 ===
1月27日，分離主義者試圖從[[戈爾洛夫卡|戈爾洛夫卡]]攻入傑巴利采韋，但遭到擊退<ref name=2dw323>{{cite news|url=http://uatoday.tv/geopolitics/militants-continue-attempt-to-take-ukraine-controlled-debaltseve-405495.html|title=Militants continue attempt to take Ukraine-controlled Debaltseve|date=2015-01-27|accessdate=2015-01-29|work=Ukraine Today|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402081551/http://uatoday.tv/geopolitics/militants-continue-attempt-to-take-ukraine-controlled-debaltseve-405495.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隔天，一名頓涅茨克軍隊的指揮官宣稱已控制能夠進城的高速公路，該城也已幾乎被包圍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfchronicle.com/news/world/article/Ukraine-says-3-soldiers-killed-in-fighting-in-the-6045479.php#/0|title=Ukraine rebels claim new key victory is within grasp|work=San Francisco Chronicle|accessdate=2015-02-02|archive-date=2015-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130162453/http://www.sfchronicle.com/news/world/article/Ukraine-says-3-soldiers-killed-in-fighting-in-the-6045479.php#/0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但是，烏克蘭議員{{link-en|德米特里·季姆丘克|Dmytro Tymchuk}}於1月29日表示分離主義者的軍隊雖然試圖切斷前線與本地的聯繫，但政府軍以砲火反擊造成其大量傷亡，分離主義者因而被迫縮減了攻勢<ref name=TYm23>{{cite news|url=http://uatoday.tv/news/debaltseve-encirclement-attempts-thwarted-by-ukrainian-artillery-405912.html|date=2015-01-29|accessdate=2015-01-29|work=Ukraine Today|title=Debaltseve encirclement attempts thwarted by Ukrainian artillery|archive-date=2016-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161026221345/http://uatoday.tv/news/debaltseve-encirclement-attempts-thwarted-by-ukrainian-artillery-405912.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[BBC_News|BBC News]]則釋出了一段親俄民兵在轟炸中被捕的影片<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-31065849|title = Footage shows pro-Russian rebels under fire in Ukraine|date = 2015-01-30|publisher = BBC News|access-date = 2015-01-30|archive-date = 2017-03-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170321031541/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-31065849|dead-url = no}}</ref>。儘管如此，同時間分離主義者奪取了距離傑巴利采韋西方約13公里的[[烏格列戈爾斯克_(烏克蘭)|烏格列戈爾斯克]]，此地正好位在{{link-en|M04高速公路 (烏克蘭)|Highway M04 (Ukraine)|M04高速公路}}從傑巴利采韋通往戈爾洛夫卡的路段上。分離主義者打破了政府軍的防線，並且佔領一座檢查哨後進入烏格列戈爾斯克，政府軍則趕緊派兵增援<ref name=232ddd>{{cite news|title=Militant tanks enter Uglegorsk, battle raging|url=http://www.unian.info/war/1037854-militant-tanks-enter-uglegorsk-fight-raging.html|agency=Ukrainian Independent Information Agency|date=2015-01-29|accessdate=2015-01-29|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806015925/https://www.unian.info/war/1037854-militant-tanks-enter-uglegorsk-fight-raging.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據[[美聯社|美聯社]]的報導指出，此城的陷落將導致政府軍守住傑巴利采韋的任務更加艱難<ref name=AP23>{{cite news|title=Russia-backed rebels overrun another town in east in onslaught against army troops|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2015/01/29/ukraine-russia-backed-rebels-overrun-another-town-in-east-in-onslaught-against/|publisher=Fox News Channel|agency=Associated Press|date=2015-01-29|accessdate=2015-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151011113656/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2015/01/29/ukraine-russia-backed-rebels-overrun-another-town-in-east-in-onslaught-against/|archive-date=2015-10-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此外，政府軍表示三名傑巴利采韋的民眾死於親俄民兵持續的轟炸<ref>{{Cite news |url =http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/01/29/us-ukraine-crisis-deathtoll-idUSKBN0L217220150129 |title =Death toll mounts in intense clashes in east Ukraine |date =2015-01-29 |agency =Reuters |access-date =2015-01-29 |archive-date =2015-10-02 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20151002215406/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/01/29/us-ukraine-crisis-deathtoll-idUSKBN0L217220150129 |dead-url =no }}</ref>。

1月30日，砲彈擊中了一輛巴士，{{link-en|古比雪夫区 (顿涅茨克)|Kuibyshevskyi District, Donetsk|古比雪夫區}}作為分發人道援助場所的一座文化中心也遭到轟炸。根據[[BBC|BBC]]的消息，許多平民和政府軍被困在城內，部分民眾則逃往政府軍「口袋」入口的[[巴赫穆特|阿爾喬莫夫斯克]]<ref name="BBC30JAN">{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-31055881 | title=Ukraine battle rages for key town of Debaltseve | publisher=BBC News | date=2015-01-30 | accessdate=2015-01-30 | archive-date=2018-11-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128124401/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-31055881 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。俄國媒體[[俄羅斯24|俄羅斯24]]報導大約有八千名政府軍仍駐留於傑巴利采韋，而分離主義者正接近關上「口袋」入口的地步。烏克蘭的地區防衛營指揮官{{link-en|谢苗·谢缅琴科|Semen Semenchenko}}表示雖然大部分地區已被親俄民兵控制，不過政府軍仍掌握著傑巴利采韋<ref name="BBC30JAN" />。烏克蘭國家安全及國防委員會發言人安德烈·李森科（Andriy Lysenko）表示援軍已經抵達烏格列戈爾斯克，仍舊守住前線<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.ukrinform.ua/eng/news/ukrainian_reinforcements_arrive_in_vuhlehirsk_where_fighting_continues_lysenko_says_328638|title = Ukrainian reinforcements arrive in Vuhlehirsk where fighting continues, Lysenko says|date = 2015-01-30|agency = Ukrinform|access-date = 2015-01-30|archive-date = 2015-02-08|archive-url = https://archive.today/20150208230016/http://www.ukrinform.ua/eng/news/ukrainian_reinforcements_arrive_in_vuhlehirsk_where_fighting_continues_lysenko_says_328638|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。在這一整天當中，分離主義者不斷向來回於阿爾喬莫夫斯克與傑巴利采韋之間的[[裝甲運兵車|裝甲運兵車]]和貨車發射[[BM-21|BM-21]]火箭炮，使得政府軍的運輸線幾乎被切斷<ref name="KP30J">{{cite news | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/separatists-gain-stranglehold-over-debaltseve-as-evacuation-continues-379003.html | title=Separatists gain stranglehold over Debaltseve as evacuation continues | work=Kyiv Post | date=2015-01-30 | accessdate=2015-01-30 | archive-date=2015-07-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150712083400/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/separatists-gain-stranglehold-over-debaltseve-as-evacuation-continues-379003.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[BM-21|BM-21]]也擊中了公寓，造成至少七位民眾喪生。剩下的居民開始搭上每天三班駛往阿爾喬莫夫斯克的巴士撤離，以躲避升級的戰火<ref name="KP30J" /><ref name=re24>{{Cite news|url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/01/30/us-ukraine-crisis-idUSKBN0L30Y220150130|title = Ukraine peace talks aborted as civilians die in east|date = 2015-01-30|agency = Reuters|access-date = 2015-01-30|archive-date = 2015-09-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924213011/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/01/30/us-ukraine-crisis-idUSKBN0L30Y220150130|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 關上「水壺」 ===
1月31日，至少十二名民眾死於分離主義者的轟炸。與此同時，政府軍為了切斷親俄民兵對烏格列戈爾斯克的援助而持續轟炸<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/12-killed-as-separatists-shell-debaltseve-379065.html|title = Kremlin-backed separatists shell Debaltseve, kill 12|date = 2015-01-31|work = Kyiv Post|access-date = 2015-01-31|archive-date = 2015-10-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151027100952/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/12-killed-as-separatists-shell-debaltseve-379065.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。[[顿巴斯营|顿巴斯营]]發動地面攻勢試圖收復該城，但以失敗收場，且造成三名士兵陣亡，部隊指揮官{{link-en|谢苗·谢缅琴科|Semen Semenchenko}}也負傷<ref name="KP1FEB">{{cite web | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/another-deadly-weekend-with-22-civilians-killed-in-donbas-379137.html | title=Another deadly weekend with 22 civilians killed in Donbas | work=Kyiv Post | date=2015-02-01 | accessdate=2015-02-01 | archive-date=2015-10-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002134532/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/another-deadly-weekend-with-22-civilians-killed-in-donbas-379137.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一方面，疏散傑巴利采韋居民的行動持續進行，該城直到當日為止無水、電及瓦斯的情況已至少十天，[[烏克蘭總理|烏克蘭總理]][[阿爾謝尼·亞采尼克|阿爾謝尼·亞采尼克]]則表示已疏散超過千位民眾<ref name="AP321">{{cite news | url=http://hosted2.ap.org/APDEFAULT/cae69a7523db45408eeb2b3a98c0c9c5/Article_2015-01-31-EU--Ukraine/id-21c944f206034ca882fc9af9090c9ec7 | title=Civilians flee east Ukraine town as fighting intensifies | date=2015-01-31 | agency=Associated Press | accessdate=2015-01-31 | author=Peter Leonard | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150202012237/http://hosted2.ap.org/APDEFAULT/cae69a7523db45408eeb2b3a98c0c9c5/Article_2015-01-31-EU--Ukraine/id-21c944f206034ca882fc9af9090c9ec7 | archivedate=2015-02-02 }}</ref>。烏克蘭國防部長{{link-en|斯捷潘·波尔托拉克|Stepan Poltorak}}證實傑巴利采韋部分地區落入分離主義者之手<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-31074772|title = Ukraine crisis: 'Dozens killed' in east as Minsk talks open|date = 2015-01-31|publisher = BBC News|access-date = 2015-01-31|archive-date = 2020-11-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108094641/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-31074772|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2月1日，政府軍在傑巴利采韋的情勢急遽惡化，根據[[基輔郵報|基輔郵報]]報導由於分離主義者推進到城市外圍一帶，[[烏克蘭民族衛隊|烏克蘭民族衛隊]]有些部隊被迫逃離<ref name="1FEB2015KP"/>。2月2日，政府軍情況仍未有起色，[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]報導分離主義者隨時可攻下與阿爾喬莫夫斯克連繫的{{link-en|M03高速公路 (烏克蘭)|Highway M03 (Ukraine)}}<ref name="1FEbNY">{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/02/02/world/rebels-set-sights-on-small-eastern-ukraine-town.html?_r=0 | title=Rebels Set Sights on Small Eastern Ukraine Town | work=The New York Times | date=2015-02-01 | accessdate=2015-02-02 | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108093138/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/02/02/world/rebels-set-sights-on-small-eastern-ukraine-town.html?_r=0 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。此路上已發生多起滿載民眾的巴士遭到砲擊的事件，使得M03高速公路幾乎等於無法通行，[[頓涅茨克人民共和國|頓涅茨克人民共和國]]領導人[[亞歷山大·弗拉基米羅維奇·扎哈爾琴科|亞歷山大·扎哈爾琴科]]也表示「任何試圖離開"水壺"地區的人將會進入我們砲擊範圍」<ref name="1FEbNY" />。一名人道援助工作者表示截至2月2日離開當地的民眾已達八千人，另名工作者則說親俄民兵刻意將攻擊目標朝向撤離居民的巴士<ref name="KP2FEB">{{cite news | url=https://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/volunteers-evacuate-residents-from-debaltseve-under-shelling-379238.html | title=Volunteers evacuate residents from Debaltseve under shelling | work=Kyiv Post | date=2015-02-02 | accessdate=2015-02-02 | archive-date=2015-11-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121044842/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/volunteers-evacuate-residents-from-debaltseve-under-shelling-379238.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。一名[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]的觀察員則形容傑巴利采韋的人道情況「災難性的」<ref name="AI3FEB">{{cite press release | url=http://www.amnesty.org/en/news/ukraine-debaltseve-s-residents-reaching-breaking-point-2015-02-03 | title=Ukraine: Debaltseve’s residents reaching breaking point | publisher=Amnesty International | date=2015-02-03 | accessdate=2015-02-03 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150218001019/http://www.amnesty.org/en/news/ukraine-debaltseve-s-residents-reaching-breaking-point-2015-02-03 | archivedate=2015-02-18 }}</ref>。而為了協助傑巴利采韋的軍隊，政府軍從[[克拉馬托爾斯克|克拉馬托爾斯克]]大量增援，其中包括了[[裝甲車|裝甲車]]及各類物資<ref name="2FEBKP">{{cite news | url=https://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/ukraine-throws-reinforcements-at-debaltseve-separatists-vow-to-escalate-war-379262.html | title=Ukraine throws reinforcements at Debaltseve, separatists vow to escalate war | work=Kyiv Post | date=2015-02-02 | accessdate=2015-02-03 | archive-date=2015-09-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908073500/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/ukraine-throws-reinforcements-at-debaltseve-separatists-vow-to-escalate-war-379262.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月3日，分離主義者與政府軍同意該天停火，以讓當地居民能夠撤離，直到[[歐洲東部時間|當地時間]]13時開始分離主義者砲火愈趨猛烈，意圖將傑巴利采韋夷為平地<ref name="3FEB20K">{{cite news | url=https://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/kremlin-backed-separatists-look-to-level-debaltseve-379386.html | title=Kremlin-backed separatists look to level Debaltseve | work=Kyiv Post | date=2015-02-03 | accessdate=2015-02-04 | archive-date=2015-10-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002190641/https://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/kremlin-backed-separatists-look-to-level-debaltseve-379386.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 評論 ==
2015年6月16日，[[VICE新聞|VICE新聞]]製作了一段23分鐘長的[[YouTube|YouTube]]報導<ref>{{youtube|2zssIFN2mso|Selfie Soldiers: Russia Checks in to Ukraine}}</ref>，追蹤和調查一名來自[[西伯利亞|西伯利亞]][[布里亞特共和國|布里亞特共和國]]的[[俄羅斯軍隊|俄軍]]士兵巴托·達姆巴耶夫（{{lang|ru|Бато Дамбаев}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Бато Дамбаев｜ВКонтакте|url=https://vk.com/batohadambaev|publisher=[[vk|vk]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401185120/https://vk.com/batohadambaev|archivedate=2015-04-01|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2015-06-22}}</ref>）的[[vk|社交網站]]相片，發現此俄軍士兵曾隨軍從俄羅斯進入烏克蘭國境，後改穿親俄份子的軍服，於[[傑巴利采韋|傑巴利采韋]]一帶上載自拍照片。報導指這次調查證明了俄軍正規部隊在烏克蘭衝突中進行了積極的干預，並認為俄軍的參與是親俄份子能夠支持至今的關鍵<ref>{{cite web|author1=Simon Ostrovsky|title=Russia Denies That Its Soldiers Are in Ukraine, But We Tracked One There Using His Selfies|url=https://news.vice.com/article/russia-denies-that-its-soldiers-are-in-ukraine-but-we-tracked-one-there-using-his-selfies|publisher=VICE News|accessdate=2015-06-22|date=2015-06-16|archive-date=2015-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622092718/https://news.vice.com/article/russia-denies-that-its-soldiers-are-in-ukraine-but-we-tracked-one-there-using-his-selfies|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

